# Privacy Policy - Download Masal Coretax

**Last Updated: 4 Maret 2025**

Thank you for using **Download Masal Coretax**. Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle your data when using our Chrome Extension.

## 1. Data Collection and Usage
**Download Masal Coretax** does not collect, store, or transmit any personal or sensitive user data. All processes are executed locally on your computer without any external data transmission. The extension solely functions to automate the clicking of the PDF download button within the Coretax platform.

## 2. Permissions and Local Processing
- This extension only interacts with Coretax by automating the clicking of buttons to facilitate bulk downloads of **Faktur Pajak Masukan, Faktur Pajak Keluaran, and Bukti Potong (Bupot)**.
- No data is sent to third-party servers or external services.
- All operations are performed on your local machine, ensuring privacy and security.

## 3. Not an Official Coretax Application
This extension is an independent tool and is **not affiliated with Coretax, any government institution, or any official tax-related service**. It is developed to complement existing features by allowing bulk downloads, a functionality not provided by Coretax natively.

## 4. No Affiliation with Coretax or Government Agencies
The **Download Masal Coretax** extension is **not endorsed by, associated with, or officially connected to Coretax or any government entity**. The use of this extension is solely at your own discretion.

## 5. Use at Your Own Risk
By using this extension, you acknowledge and agree that you are using it at your own risk (**DYOR - Do Your Own Research**). The developer is not responsible for any issues, including but not limited to:
- Changes to Coretax that may affect the functionality of this extension.
- Any potential restrictions or policy updates from Coretax.
- Any consequences arising from the use of this extension.

## 6. Updates and Changes
This Privacy Policy may be updated periodically to reflect any changes in functionality, compliance, or other necessary modifications. Users are encouraged to review this document regularly.

## 7. Contact Information
If you have any questions or concerns regarding this Privacy Policy, please contact us at: **jitu@jituleads.com**.

